</u></strong></font></td>\r\n      <td></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Breakfast</td>\r\n      <td>7:00 AM-9:00 AM</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>POP &amp; Prototype Open Review for Buyers &amp; VIA Sponsors</td>\r\n      <td>7:00 AM-8:00 AM</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Appointments: Session III</td>\r\n      <td>8:30 AM-11:30 AM</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Lunch</td>\r\n      <td>11:30 AM-12:30PM</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>POP &amp; Prototype Open Review for Buyers &amp; VIA Sponsors</td>\r\n      <td>11:30 AM-12:30PM</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Appointments: Session lV</td>\r\n      <td>12:30 PM-4:30 PM</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Bonus Time</td>\r\n      <td>4:30 PM-5:30 PM</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td bgcolor=\"#000000\"></td>\r\n      <td bgcolor=\"#000000\"></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td><font size=\"3\"><strong><u>THURSDAY, JUNE 13th,\r\n        2013</u></strong></font></td>\r\n      <td></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Breakfast</td>\r\n      <td>7:00 AM-9:00 AM</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>POP &amp; Prototype Open Review for Buyers &amp; VIA Sponsors</td>\r\n      <td>8:30 AM-11:30 AM</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>Appointments: Session V </td>\r\n      <td>8:30 AM-11:30 AM</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>POP &amp; New Product Preview Break-Down</td>\r\n      <td>11:30 AM-2:00 PM</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </tbody>\r\n</table>','NLGS Tentative Schedule','','inherit','open','open','','35-revision-v1','','','2013-08-06 15:34:29','2013-08-06 15:34:29','',35,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?p=36',0,'revision','',0),(37,1,'2013-08-06 15:35:11','2013-08-06 15:35:11',' <img src=\"/sites/all/themes/NLGS2010/images/content/travel.png\" />\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center\">\r\n  <table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\" cellpadding=\"10\" width=\"100%\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td width=\"175px\" height=\"95px\"><img src=\"/sites/all/themes/nlgshow_core/images/NLGS-Logo.gif\" border=\"0\" /></td>\r\n        <td><p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\r\n            The National Lawn &amp; Garden Show <br />\r\n            will be held June 11-13, 2013<br />\r\n            Crowne Plaza Chicago O’Hare Hotel &amp;<br />Conference Center, Rosemont, IL</span></strong></p></td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n  </table>\r\n  </td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  </tbody>\r\n  </table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><strong><u>ARRIVAL  &amp; DEPARTURE INFORMATION</u></strong><br />\r\n  Vendors will need to make your airfare arrangements to arrive at the  hotel no later than 1:00 PM on Monday, (Buyers may arrive as late as 3PM) June  10, 2013.  Your appointments could last  until 11:30 AM on Thursday, June 13th, so please book your return  flight accordingly. </strong><strong>You may  schedule your return flight anytime after 1:00 PM</strong>, Thursday, June 13th.  Appointments will run June 11th  – 13th for all NLGS buyers and vendors.<br /><br />\r\n  \r\n  <strong><u>Check-in &amp; P.O.P &amp;  Prototype Set-up:</u></strong><br />\r\n Check-in and POP/Prototype Display set-up will start at 10:00 AM and end  at 4:00 PM on Monday, June 10th.  <u>POP &amp; Prototype set up must be completed by 4:00 PM, as buyers  will have access to preview the POP area and evaluate the Prototype area.</u>  No exceptions please!</p>\r\n \r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><u>Hotel Accommodations:  Crowne  Plaza Chicago  O&rsquo;Hare Hotel &amp; Conference Center, Rosemont,   IL</u>:</strong><br />\r\n  5440 North River Road, Rosemont,   IL 60018. <a href=\"http://www.crowneplazaohare.com\" target=\"_blank\">www.crowneplazaohare.com</a></u> Register by clicking the link:<br />\r\n  <a href=\"https://resweb.passkey.com/Resweb.do?mode=welcome_ei_new&amp;eventID=9943616\" target=\"_blank\">https://resweb.passkey.com/Resweb.do?mode=welcome_ei_new&amp;eventID=9943616</a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Booking  Code:NLF you will get a confirmation number upon completion of your reservation,  or by calling 877-337-5793 or central reservations at 843-760-5839 (Toll  Free).  The negotiated room rate is $135.00  single or double occupancy.  You must  mention the &ldquo;National Lawn &amp; Garden Show&rdquo; Booking code: NLF to get the  discounted room rate.  Please ask the  hotel about its reservation &amp; cancellation policies.  Please call by May 31, 2013, 8 PM CST to  guarantee the discounted rate.  After  this date please call 888-233-9534 and we will make every effort to secure the  discount, however prevailing rates will apply and rates are as high as $220 per  night. <strong>There are several events taking  place in our timeframe at the Rosemont   Convention Center so rooms  will be scarce, please reserve early. </strong><br /><br />\r\n  <strong><u>Complimentary Hotel Shuttle  Service to/from O&rsquo;Hare Airport</u></strong>:  <br />The hotel is 10 minutes from O&rsquo;Hare airport. The Crowne  Plaza O\'Hare provides a 24 hour complimentary airport shuttle to and from  O&rsquo;Hare International Airport. Crowne Plaza&rsquo;s pickup location for domestic travelers in  O\'Hare is at Door 2 of the Shuttle   Bus Center.  International travelers please use the courtesy phones in the baggage area to  contact the hotel to schedule a pick-up. From Midway Airport use rental car or  book with private limo or cab as no complimentary service is available.<br /><br />\r\n  Discount  Car Rental rates: We have negotiated special rates with Thrifty Car  Rental.&nbsp; The special code is valid throughout the year and  nationwide.&nbsp; Use Corporate Discount Code 004M002073 at <a href=\"http://www.thrifty.com\" target=\"_blank\">www.thrifty.com</a> or call 1-800-THRIFTY  (847-4389) (US &amp; Canada) or 1-918-669-2168 (outside US and Canada). Or go  to <a href=\"http://www.thrifty.com/reservations/index.aspx?corpnum=004M002073\" target=\"_blank\">www.thrifty.com/reservations/index.aspx?corpnum=004M002073</a><br /><br />\r\n  <strong><u>Driving Directions</u></strong><strong>: </strong><br /><strong>From O&rsquo;Hare  Airport.</strong> Head East on I-190, for 2 miles to River    Road. Turn right on River Road and proceed down to 5440 N. River Road,  directly across from the convention center. <br /><strong>From the East (Chicago).</strong> Take I90  West to 190 (O&rsquo;Hare exit) continue 15 miles to River Road exit. Turn right on River Road and  proceed to 5440 N. River Road  directly across from the convention center. <br /><strong>From the West (Rockford).</strong> Take I90 East to Chicago. Exit on Cumberland Road North.  Go right on Cumberland,  2 blocks to 1st light (Higgins/Rt.72). Go left on Higgins and proceed 1 mile to  River Road.  Go left on River Road  and proceed to 5440 N. River Road  directly across from the Convention Center. <br /><strong>From the South (Indiana).</strong> Take 294  North (Wisconsin)  and follow signs to 190 (O&rsquo;Hare exit). Take 190 to River Road (1st light). Go right on River Road and  proceed to 5440 N. River Road  directly across from the Convention Center. <br /><strong>From the North (Wisconsin).</strong> Take 294 South  to 190 East, follow signs to O&rsquo;Hare. Pay at toll. Stay in the right lane. Exit Mannheim Road South.  Get back on the highway and follow signs to Chicago. Exit River Road South. Turn Right. Hotel  is on the right side, approximately 2 blocks down. <br /><br />\r\n  <strong><u>Opening  Reception</u>:</strong><br />\r\n  Please note that all participants are expected to be at the Hotel on  Monday, June 10th, at 6:00 PM for Dinner Reception and Orientation  Meeting.<br /><br />\r\n  <strong><u>Emergency Contact:</u></strong><br />\r\n  Appointments will begin at 8:30 AM on Tuesday, June 11th, and  will conclude on Thursday June 13th at 11:30 AM. Please  fax emergency contact information to 719-488-8168 in case we need to contact you during the event.</p>','NLGS Venue & Travel Info.','','publish','open','open','','nlgs-venue-travel-info','','','2013-08-06 15:35:11','2013-08-06 15:35:11','',0,'http://wordpress.nlgshow.com/?page_id=37',0,'page','',0),(38,1,'2013-08-06 15:35:11','2013-08-06 15:35:11',' <img src=\"/sites/all/themes/NLGS2010/images/content/travel.png\" />\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center\">\r\n  <table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\" cellpadding=\"10\" width=\"100%\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td width=\"175px\" height=\"95px\"><img src=\"/sites/all/themes/nlgshow_core/images/NLGS-Logo.gif\" border=\"0\" /></td>\r\n        <td><p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\r\n            The National Lawn &amp; Garden Show <br />\r\n            will be held June 11-13, 2013<br />\r\n            Crowne Plaza Chicago O’Hare Hotel &amp;<br />Conference Center, Rosemont, IL</span></strong></p></td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n  </table>\r\n  </td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  </tbody>\r\n  </table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><strong><u>ARRIVAL  &amp; DEPARTURE INFORMATION</u></strong><br />\r\n  Vendors will need to make your airfare arrangements to arrive at the  hotel no later than 1:00 PM on Monday, (Buyers may arrive as late as 3PM) June  10, 2013.  Your appointments could last  until 11:30 AM on Thursday, June 13th, so please book your return  flight accordingly. </strong><strong>You may  schedule your return flight anytime after 1:00 PM</strong>, Thursday, June 13th.  Appointments will run June 11th  – 13th for all NLGS buyers and vendors.<br /><br />\r\n  \r\n  <strong><u>Check-in &amp; P.O.P &amp;  Prototype Set-up:</u></strong><br />\r\n Check-in and POP/Prototype Display set-up will start at 10:00 AM and end  at 4:00 PM on Monday, June 10th.  <u>POP &amp; Prototype set up must be completed by 4:00 PM, as buyers  will have access to preview the POP area and evaluate the Prototype area.</u>  No exceptions please!</p>\r\n \r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><u>Hotel Accommoda